l/20210505/RYHJ3KU7KNHTRJPB5CBJ6CYAPQ/</a>"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:15:02.000Z","msg":"根據《NBC NEWS》報導，這名女子去年11月25日在一個峽谷中失蹤，但憑著「機智」，活到現在。她告訴警方，為了生存，她以草和青苔做為食物，喝的則是河邊取來的水；<span class=\"red\">另外，有部分的食物則是靠路過登山客所提供</span>。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:27:50.000Z","msg":"年輕人靠自己儲的10萬和爸爸俾的90萬得首期"},{"pid":"180f763481974144e0c8e292ce4f59dcaf4030e8","tid":2517800,"uid":278712,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:30:48.000Z","msg":"<strong>「原本警方是使用無人機搜尋，但無人機墜毁，搜救人員為了尋找無人機，而看到一頂帳篷」</strong><br />\n<br />\n無人機用生命完成了任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a4df6bc6000b64a136ae858437e7fcdfd1e355","tid":2517800,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598ee4dd5bc861e4efdbd6560c0eac4e397d92c0","tid":2517800,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"988bbb670ae4844d80da69b484dfdb008ec715f3","tid":2517800,"uid":191453,"like":10,"dislike":10,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:13:58.000Z","msg":"牛b<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(生物)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"cow ur motherfucker B"},{"pid":"b5641b03640a6f89294873e1647b0f1c926c36a9","tid":2517800,"uid":108756,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"3d63210a88fe1c7d8a8658dad3624b068a6add1c","tid":2517800,"uid":358141,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"quote":{"pid":"9c647eaae54531775337d95adef4adc0c3b7c142","tid":2517800,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JCtE0km.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJCtE0km.png&h=c6924bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國猶他州1名47歲女子，從去年底失蹤，竟然靠著吃草和青苔過了6個月，而且渡過寒冬，日前平安的被當地警方給尋獲。<br />\n<br />\n根據《