方表示，當地冬天氣溫經常降到零度以下，很好奇她只靠帳篷、吃草和飲用河水能活下來。據了解，這名女子精神方面可能些問題，因為聽說她是自願留在峽谷的，搜救人員已送她到醫院接受治療和心理上的評估。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210505/RYHJ3KU7KNHTRJPB5CBJ6CYAPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210505%2FRYHJ3KU7KNHTRJPB5CBJ6CYAPQ%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn2rU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=9db05381\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210505%2FRYHJ3KU7KNHTRJPB5CBJ6CYAPQ%2F&h=5a3e3334\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210505/RYHJ3KU7KNHTRJPB5CBJ6CYAPQ/</a>"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:15:02.000Z","msg":"根據《NBC NEWS》報導，這名女子去年11月25日在一個峽谷中失蹤，但憑著「機智」，活到現在。她告訴警方，為了生存，她以草和青苔做為食物，喝的則是河邊取來的水；<span class=\"red\">另外，有部分的食物則是靠路過登山客所提供</span>。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e847d8629613636073ce741b14d53ec953b9970e","tid":2517800,"uid":38588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c245870e885210f257369a759f6969195d08b1d","tid":2517800,"uid":227271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"c1ce13e678db0b778aa8fc7817f530139a2c4260","tid":2517800,"uid":123774,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"b11abeb2ed66cc79e4a97366c80cb0646e799456","tid":2517800,"uid":50423,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:16:23.000Z","msg":"登山客經過唔求救?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:18:30.000Z","msg":"這名女子精神方面可能些問題<br />\n因為聽說她是自願留在峽谷的"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uYV0KPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuYV0KPU.jpg&h=478fa01a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"自願？何謂自願呀大佬？"},{